{
  "texts": [
    "Water samples from the start and end of the experiment were analyzed by Waters Agricultural Laboratories (Camilla, GA).",
    "Further details of the growth conditions, tissue analysis, and water analysis can be found in supporting documentation (S 1.1).",
    "Plant growth was continuously monitored using a WIFI-connected (Simple Mobile Moxee 4G Mobile Hotspot, Simple Mobile; Miami, USA) imaging system (RAYN Vision Systems, Middletown, USA).",
    "Overhead multispectral images were captured every hour beginning at 10 pm (eight images per night) using five MSI cameras from 4 days after transplanting (DAT), for a total of 880 overhead images.",
    "The MSI output included 1,280 x 800-pixel images with a depth of 10 channels (blue, cyan, green, amber, red, deep red, far red, NIR-850 and NIR-940)."
  ]
}